### Hadith 1:131

*Narrated Anas:*

I was informed that the Prophet had said to Mu'adh, "Whosoever will meet
Allah without associating anything in worship with Him will go to
Paradise." Mu'adh asked the Prophet, "Should I not inform the people of
this good news?" The Prophet replied, "No, I am afraid, lest they should
depend upon it (absolutely)."

